<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很久很久以前， 有一位国王和他的王后，非常想要一个孩子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，日子一天天过去了， 他们一直没有孩子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>慢慢地，国王失去了耐心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46757</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的王后！”一天，国王对王后抱怨说，“我们需要一个孩子！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46758</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49975</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他国王都有孩子，而且很多！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49975</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54150</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>知道吗？有一个国王竟然有12个孩子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54151</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62592</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王后扬了扬眉毛：“12个孩子吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拍了拍国王的胳膊，“我们也会有的，要有耐心。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王一边走一边叹气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75313</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王宫外面有一个美丽的湖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王心情不好的时候，沿着湖边散散步，心情就会好很多。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，王后就生了一个孩子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“多么漂亮的小公主！”国王非常高兴，“我们就叫她艾伦吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99354</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103808</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王和王后开始为孩子的洗礼做准备。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108012</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王负责写请柬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108012</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是他太着急了， 不小心忘了一个人 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他忘了邀请他的姐姐艾格尼丝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116800</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122393</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你可能会感到惊讶 ，国王怎么会忘记邀请自己的姐姐呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其实，这些年，国王一直都在努力地让自己忘记她！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>忘记这个脾气不好，而且十分恶毒的女人！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>事实上，没有人喜欢艾格尼丝，就连她的黑猫也不喜欢她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的额头很大，脸上全是难看的皱纹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147284</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当她生气时，眼睛会闪着蓝光；</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当她非常生气时，眼睛会闪着黄色和绿色的光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163064</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哦！艾格尼丝还有一个大家都不知道的秘密。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她是一个女巫—— 一个非常邪恶的女巫！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>公主出生的消息传遍了整个王国。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“王宫里将会举行一场特别的洗礼。”艾格尼丝说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也会被邀请的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190634</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾格尼丝每天都查看她的信件。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是每天的结果都一样——没有来自国王的请柬！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210273</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哼！”艾格尼丝生气地跺了跺脚，“希望我的弟弟没有忘记我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210273</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于到了洗礼的日子。艾格尼丝也终于下定了决心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230040</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有请柬我也要去！”艾格尼丝穿上她最好的衣服，上了马车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马车走向王宫，艾格尼丝的眼睛闪着黄色和绿色的光，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等着瞧！我那无礼的弟弟再也不会忘记我了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>